<paragraph id="IFRS17_B110" base="F55667569"><paranum>B110</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="B110"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P0886">For <xref base="F55666959" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_TE0009">insurance contracts with direct participation features<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0187"/></ph></xref>, the <xref base="F55666917" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0519">contractual service margin<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0052"/></ph></xref> is adjusted to reflect the variable nature of the fee. Hence, changes in the amounts set out in <xref id="IFRS17_X0712" base="F59236538" href="IFRS17_B104.dita#IFRS17_B104">paragraph B104</xref> are treated as set out in <xref id="IFRS17_X0713" base="F59236539" href="IFRS17_B111.dita#IFRS17_B111">paragraphs B111&#x2013;B114</xref>.</p><p id="IFRS17_P0888"/></body></paragraph>